## 3. Performance — sim must not lag the browser

**Mistakes made:**

| Mistake | Symptom | Fix |
|---------|---------|-----|
| `setSamples(prev => [...prev, s])` every 20 ms | Unbounded array, O(n²) copies, full React tree re-render | Sim owns ring buffer; `subscribe()` + rAF for viz |
| Slider calls `patchConstant` + Monaco on every mousemove | Multi-second freeze during kG binary search | `setConfig` immediate; debounce code patch (~150 ms) + flush on pointer up |
| GraphPanel `.map()` new arrays every tick | GC pressure | Preallocated `Float64Array`, reuse uPlot buffers |
| Physics tied to render rate | Jitter | Physics at fixed `DT` (20 ms); render at display rate |

**Rule:** The sim loop must **never** trigger a React state update per physics step. Mechanism canvas and TraceView update imperatively via refs + `requestAnimationFrame`.

**Rule:** `React.memo` on SpringTune, BenchScope, SimControlsBar.

